\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs third-party vendor engagements.
 It establishes Supply Chain Risk Management (SCRM) controls for the acquisition of technology products and services.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*

\lang english
2.
 Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy applies to all third-party entities —
 including vendors,
 contractors,
 consultants,
 and managed service providers (MSPs) —
 that interact with Elko County information systems,
 data,
 or secure facilities.
 This policy does not govern commodity off-the-shelf consumables (e.g.,
 toner,
 cables) where the vendor has no access to County systems,
 data,
 or secure facilities.
\end_layout

