\series bold
Contractor-Owned Device Support
\series default
:
 Information Operations Personnel shall not troubleshoot,
 configure,
 or install software on contractor-owned devices.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Clarification
\series default
:
 The Information Operations Department may provide County-approved secure access software (e.g.,
 VPN clients,
 MFA agents) as artifacts to the contractor,
